{"tid":210460,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宮崎葵「超短髮」震撼日本鄉民！群情崩潰：蘿莉變歐巴桑","createTime":"2017-04-21T03:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T01:05:50.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"245a0e0d9ee0ded31aa8441147240a12fdad185b","tid":210460,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"日本女星宮崎葵以超短髮拍攝知名紅茶飲料廣告，廣告配樂還選用《一休和尚》的主題歌，立刻掀起熱烈討論。她出道以來大多以長髮示人，雖然會因戲修剪長度，但是首度將頭髮剪到耳上，並露出半個額頭，實用面積310至497平方呎，平均呎價16,055元。新髮型引來網友兩極評價，有人覺得超可愛，有人認為不合適，甚至撞臉資深女星大竹忍。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2471/d2471373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2471%2Fd2471373.jpg&h=64a75e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ▲宮崎葵「超短髮」亮相，日本鄉民崩潰了。<br />\n<br />\n廣告中，宮崎葵在充滿歐洲風情的火車站中，西裝外套內搭紅色針織衫，配上卡其色裙子，相較於其他乘客腳步迅速，她則悄悄到轉角喝起飲料，告訴自己「不急不急，休息一下。」拍攝空檔她露出燦爛笑容，和工作人員溝通十分親切，發現有攝影機在拍，雙手擺在腿上正坐的POSE相當可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2471/d2471367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2471%2Fd2471367.jpg&h=f79644ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宮崎葵全新髮型拍廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2471/d2471370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2471%2Fd2471370.jpg&h=ea2859f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宮崎葵超短髮掀起兩派爭議。<br />\n<br />\n網友看到宮崎葵新髮型，直言「馬上想到大竹忍」、「本來很漂亮的，感覺很可惜耶。」還有人難掩震驚，形容「像國會議員」、「為什麼經紀公司不阻止」、「就像一向留長髮的人突然變短就成歐巴桑了。」部分粉絲力挺「還是很可愛啊」、「感覺很有個性」，此外也有人認為女神可能只是戴假髮，各種意見在網路展開激烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2471/d2471369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2471%2Fd2471369.jpg&h=e21c569e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宮崎葵超短髮，網友聯想到資深女星大竹忍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ct3ostaK-u0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fct3ostaK-u0&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1d62ceab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ct3ostaK-u0</a><br />\n▲宮崎葵超短髮造型掀起網友議論。"},{"pid":"058669778c8eb7ccc94f414fdde5807091595964","tid":210460,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:09:36.000Z","msg":"女仔冇咁上下面型同5官都唔好學人剪短髮"},{"pid":"5187dbf858c1b5181a2dcba904431cc5864c2421","tid":210460,"uid":65144,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"但是首度將頭髮剪到耳上，並露出半個額頭，實用面積310至497平方呎，平均呎價16,055元。"},{"pid":"10cd01484667739d6964ddbc05d048515a5fb787","tid":210460,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"唔差<br />\n但長尸"},{"pid":"a4c5a1934bf3607bbe3dd493867041372ecc75ad","tid":210460,"uid":17781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但是首度將頭髮剪到耳上，並露出半個額頭，實用面積310至497平方呎，平均呎價16,055元。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7688961850fc8362113499db14c6ada606e8f5ba","tid":210460,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"唔差喎"},{"pid":"5bc3c098c07aff6aa412dee002959bccbdb503c3","tid":210460,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但是首度將頭髮剪到耳上，並露出半個額頭，實用面積310至497平方呎，平均呎價16,055元。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc81a9131032e2eb9b1ebe9c5b41c964f3d8223","tid":210460,"uid":32081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"睇錯宮崎駿，係咪我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi